      • loadWebResponse

        public void loadWebResponse(com.gargoylesoftware.htmlunit.WebRequest webRequest)
                     throws java.lang.Exception
        Loads the WebResponse corresponding to the WebRequest.
        If WebRequest.isXHR() is false, it loads the SgmlPage and sets the WebResponse.
        If WebRequest.isXHR() is true, it only sets the WebResponse.
